04d8ff56-72db-43eb-a5be-13525349c1cf.description:
[h1] Duck Character [/h1]

This mod adds Duck character to the game, they spawn near Wocs

[h1] FEATURES:[/h1]
[list]
[*] They spawn around Wocs and try to stay close to them
[*] They will follow you if you hold a corn
[*] They will eat corn and drop a cotton
[*] They will die after 30 in-game days if not fed
[*] They are staying around an area they were last fed
[*] Have full set of animations
[/list]
[h1] How to use it: [/h1] 
[b]1. Copy this into: SM game/Survival/Character/characterdatabase.json under first { symbol[/b]
[code]
	"71f83419-88c0-4131-aa20-25334586fae2": // Duck
	{
		"renderables": [ "$CONTENT_04d8ff56-72db-43eb-a5be-13525349c1cf/Character/Duck/duck.rend" ],
		"ragdoll": "",
		"tumble":{
			"col": "$GAME_DATA/Objects/Collision/obj_decor_mannequinhand.obj",
			"offset": [0.0, 0.0, 0.833],"mass": 75.0
		},
		"hit":{
			"stand":{
				"col": "$GAME_DATA/Objects/Collision/obj_decor_mannequinhand.obj",
				"offset": [0.0, 0.0, 0.0]
			}
		},
		"unit":{
			"scriptPath": "$CONTENT_04d8ff56-72db-43eb-a5be-13525349c1cf/Scripts/DuckUnit.lua",
			"scriptClass": "DuckUnit","data": {}
		},
		"character": {
			"scriptPath": "$CONTENT_04d8ff56-72db-43eb-a5be-13525349c1cf/Scripts/DuckCharacter.lua",
			"scriptClass": "DuckCharacter","data": {}
		},
		"movement":{
			"moveSpeed": 0.15,"slowDownSpeed": 0.15,"crouchSpeed": 0.15,
			"sprintSpeed": 0.30,"jumpImpulse": 0.30,
			"headingRotationSpeed": 8.1415,"facingRotationSpeed": 8.1415,
			"mass": 75.0,"canSwim": true
		},
		"capsule": { "radius": 0.3,"height": 0.7,"crouchHeight": 0.7 }
	},
[/code]
[b]2. Open SM game/Survival/Scripts/game/survival_spawns.lua and search for:[/b]
[code]elseif tag == "WOC" then[/code]
[b]3. Under it, add this line:[/b]
[code]
sm.unit.createUnit(sm.uuid.new("71f83419-88c0-4131-aa20-25334586fae2"),sm.vec3.new(node.position.x+5,node.position.y,node.position.z+2),toYaw( node.rotation ) )
[/code]

You can add multiple lines of code above to spawn a lot more Ducks

